The report shows that the inventory system handled customer requests efficiently with minimal 
queue formation and no significant waiting time. Since multiple workers were available, 
most requests were processed immediately. The worker utilization was low, indicating that the system 
had sufficient processing capacity for the incoming inventory demands.
